data.description: Find your Home Oasis here! Assumable 3% VA loan available for vets. Spacious, open-concept living w/ high ceilings, Island-style kitchen w/ granite counters, stainless appliances, beautiful ebonized hardwood, pantry. Main floor office, 3-car tandem garage w/ drop zone cubbies just inside, 4 bed, 3 bath. Owner's suite features Luxury 5-piece bath, large walk-in closet, plenty of room. New roof, exterior paint & east windows installed this year. Extended back yard patio, 6' privacy fencing, exterior security cameras included & the high-end whole-house water filtration system. Small HOA fee and NO metro district! With local boutiques, restaurants, stores & many seasonal community festivals/events, this home is not just a place to live, it's a lifestyle. Whether you're relaxing on the patio in the shaded afternoon, working from home, entertaining guests, taking walks in the park or trails or taking in the back-range Rocky Mountain views, this property provides a unique blend of tranquility, comfort & a more rural charm all while having the convenience of many nearby city amenities. This is your next home!
